# CODEOWNERS — auto-routes review for security-critical paths.
# Format: <pattern> <owner> [<owner> ...]
# Owners: GitHub usernames or @org/team slugs.

# Default — at least one ops reviewer on everything
*  @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops

# Security-sensitive infrastructure
/.github/                @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
/.github/workflows/      @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
/.github/CODEOWNERS      @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/prod-admins
/.github/dependabot.yml  @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops

# Auth, sessions, API client, security headers
**/auth/**               @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/session.server.*      @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/firebase*.server.*    @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/firebase*.client.*    @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/api/client.*          @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/lib/api.*             @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/headers.*             @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/_headers              @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/nginx*.conf           @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/Dockerfile            @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops
**/docker-compose*.yml   @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/devops

# Production deletion / cutover
/CUTOVER.md              @luiza-prog  @marquee-ai/prod-admins
